history.content:
Girls Who Code @ Berkeley invites you to join us for our NFT Workshop this Wednesday, April 13 in Hearst Field Annex, Room B1 from 6:10 PM - 7:00 PM PST!! 💫

Come check out our NFT workshop where we will create digital art and learn how to upload/create our own NFTs!

📍WHERE: Hearst Field Annex, Room B1
🕕WHEN: Wednesday, April 13 from 6:10 PM - 7:00 PM

For more information, Check out our Facebook and Instagram @gwcberkeley
